hifiberry-webui (0.7) stable; urgency=medium

  * Enhanced lyrics display with synchronized highlighting and auto-scrolling
  * Implemented smart scrolling with comfort zones for optimal lyrics positioning
  * Added shared usePlayerPosition composable for consistent time tracking
  * Updated audio controls to use shared position calculation logic
  * Improved lyrics overlay with larger, centered text and better spacing
  * Added support for timed vs untimed lyrics detection
  * Enhanced UI consistency with shared SCSS button mixins
  * Prevented highlighting of empty lyrics lines
  * Removed debug output for cleaner console logs

 -- HiFiBerry <info@hifiberry.com>  Thu, 24 Jul 2025 12:00:00 +0000

